*background:   rgb:00/00/00
*foreground:   rgb:ff/ff/ff
!
*color0:       rgb:30/30/30
*color7:       rgb:c0/c0/c0
*color8:       rgb:80/80/80
*color15:      rgb:df/df/df
!
*color1:       rgb:ff/40/40
*color2:       rgb:40/ff/40
*color3:       rgb:ff/ff/40
*color4:       rgb:40/40/ff
*color5:       rgb:ff/40/ff
*color6:       rgb:40/ff/ff
!
*color9:       rgb:ff/80/80
*color10:      rgb:80/ff/80
*color11:      rgb:ff/ff/80
*color12:      rgb:80/80/ff
*color13:      rgb:ff/80/ff
